==Arabic==
===Etynology===
From the root verb {{ARchar|[[رحب]]}} (ráħiba), to be wide, and {{ARchar|[[رحب]]}} (ráħħaba), to make welcome, to receive graciously.

===Adverb===
'''{{ARchar|مرحبًا}}''' (marħában)

# [[hello]], [[welcome]] ''(greeting)''

===Related terms===
*{{ARchar|[[رحب]]}} (ráħiba, to welcome)

